description: Try our easy to follow Chicken, Leek & Veggie Bake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chicken, Leek & Veggie Bake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 450 g Macro Organic frozen cauliflower florets

recipeInstructions.text: Place peas in a food processor and process until roughly crushed. Transfer to a bowl and add cauliflower, tossing to combine. Top chicken mixture with pea mixture, then bake for 55 minutes or until golden. Serve.
